instead of preparing for the coronation ceremony?

56
00:02:57,030 --> 00:02:58,579
[Unworldly Doctor, Mr. Tushan]

57
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,630
You live in a simple cottage,

58
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:01,710
yet you see the world.

59
00:03:01,730 --> 00:03:03,120
I admire that.

60
00:03:03,220 --> 00:03:05,080
I humbly ask for your help,

61
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,190
