don't need anything.

64
00:03:08,670 --> 00:03:09,400
This old man,

65
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:09,680
what's your...

66
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,280
Han Qi!

67
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,850
The safety of His Highness concerns the fate of the entire nation.

68
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,579
I implore you to lend your aid.

69
00:03:21,610 --> 00:03:22,980
For the rest of my life,

70
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:25,450
I wish only to live peacefully in this humble cottage

71
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:26,760
among the green hills.

72
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:28,520
I have no interest

73
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,010
in worldly affairs.

74
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:31,930
If you refuse to help,

75
00:03:32,579 --> 00:03:35,030
I will kneel here and not rise.

76
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,490
I've seen too many

77
00:03:38,550 --> 00:03:40,510
people like you.

78
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,630
How about this?

79
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,760
I have

80
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:46,940
an unsolved game of chess

81
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,829
that has troubled me for three years.

82
00:03:48,850 --> 00:03:50,620
If you can solve it,

83
00:03:50,829 --> 00:03:52,120
I'll consider your request.

84
00:03:58,380 --> 00:03:59,450
Shared liberties are long,

85
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:00,590
external liberties are short,

86
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:03,010
and the outcome of the fight depends on who has eyes.

87
00:04:04,150 --> 00:04:05,240
Single stone connection,

88
00:04:05,410 --> 00:04:06,830
extending in the air,

89
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:09,450
three stones and two turns, extending one liberty.

90
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:12,110
Do not be greedy for victory.

91
00:04:12,130 --> 00:04:13,730
Enter enemy territory cautiously.

92
00:04:13,900 --> 00:04:15,400
When attacking, consider both the enemy and yourself.

93
00:04:16,029 --> 00:04:17,800
Sacrifice stones to gain the initiative.

94
00:04:33,450 --> 00:04:34,620
Marvelous.

95
00:04:34,650 --> 00:04:36,440
Truly marvelous.

96
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:39,380
Indeed, she's no ordinary woman.

97
00:04:48,490 --> 00:04:49,909
Advancing by retreating.

98
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,140
Northern Zhao

99
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:52,590
has hope.

100
00:04:54,510 --> 00:04:56,120
Please, sir, show us the way.

101
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,820
How did it go?

102
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,930
Do you have a solution?

103
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:08,890
What are the conditions?

104
00:05:13,570 --> 00:05:14,730
Going to Mount Qianren

105
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,860
to find him a sacred herb, Autumn Frost Grass, which is known

106
00:05:16,890 --> 00:05:17,930
to be highly poisonous.

107
00:05:19,350 --> 00:05:20,720
The king of all poisons?

108
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:22,120
They grow in clusters

109
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,680
and look like ordinary plants.

110
00:05:23,850 --> 00:05:24,800
Only by tasting them personally

111
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,680
can one tell the difference.

112
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:29,310
But testers usually fall into two extremes—

113
00:05:29,810 --> 00:05:31,300
either they can only tell the truth,

114
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:34,030
or their internal organs are torn apart, and they die instantly.

115
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,280
That old man is ruthless.

116
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,540
As long as it can save his life,

117
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,190
even at the risk of my own,

118
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,570
I will give it a try.

119
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,490
Your Highness,

120
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,390
let's go.

121
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:02,610
Your Highness.

122
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:10,790
[Mount Qianren]

123
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:13,270
Autumn Frost Grass?

124
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:14,720
Where are we supposed to find it

125
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,580
in this desolate place?

126
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:16,990
You talk too much.

127
00:06:17,010 --> 00:06:18,610
Persistence pays off.

128
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,930
Just keep looking.

129
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,300
Si,

130
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:56,470
why are we back where we started?

131
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:00,560
Where are His Highness and Shisan?

132
00:07:01,030 --> 00:07:01,980
How should I know?

133
00:07:02,010 --> 00:07:03,390
I should be the one asking you.

134
00:07:03,410 --> 00:07:05,280
Weren't you the one taking care of them from behind,

135
00:07:05,310 --> 00:07:07,160
while I'm the one leading the way up front?

136
00:07:08,210 --> 00:07:08,830
Come on.

137
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:10,000
How can you push

138
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,390
all the blame onto me?

139
00:07:11,410 --> 00:07:12,620
You're so unreliable.

140
00:07:12,650 --> 00:07:13,680
I... I... I...

141
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:15,860
Your Highness!

142
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:16,920
Your Highness!

143
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:19,110
Si?

144
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:22,270
Han Qi?

145
00:07:27,890 --> 00:07:28,880
Your Highness!

146
00:07:29,150 --> 00:07:30,200
Your Highness!

147
00:07:30,230 --> 00:07:31,280
Your Highness!

148
00:07:31,410 --> 00:07:32,500
Your Highness!

149
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,240
Prince Yu!

150
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:35,390
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

151
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,250
Han Qi?

152
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:41,800
Han Qi!

153
00:07:44,290 --> 00:07:45,409
Your Highness, be careful!

154
00:08:02,060 --> 00:08:02,780
Xu Hanzhi?

155
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:04,000
Xu Hanzhi!

156
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,310
It's all my fault.

157
00:08:05,330 --> 00:08:06,060
It's all my fault.

158
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:12,790
The leaves of Autumn Frost Grass

159
00:08:12,810 --> 00:08:14,100
resemble shields.

160
00:08:14,350 --> 00:08:15,900
This one looks like it.

161
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:35,039
Shisan.

162
00:08:37,020 --> 00:08:37,830
Shisan.

163
00:08:38,850 --> 00:08:39,850
Don't.

164
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:41,380
When did you find out?

165
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:43,440
I knew it from the very beginning.

166
00:08:43,470 --> 00:08:45,490
Looking at people is never done with the eyes,

167
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:46,600
but with the heart.

168
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,950
The Autumn Frost Grass.

169
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:54,370
I found it.

170
00:09:00,930 --> 00:09:01,830
Shisan,

171
00:09:01,890 --> 00:09:04,090
I know you didn't mean to hurt my eyes.

172
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:05,630
That was because of the secret technique,

173
00:09:05,770 --> 00:09:06,600
right?

174
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:11,040
I also know that all you care about is revenge,

175
00:09:11,450 --> 00:09:12,980
but please don't push me away,

176
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:14,850
okay?

177
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,020
Okay.

178
00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:18,350
It's the feeling of my internal organs being torn apart.

179
00:09:18,850 --> 00:09:20,300
I found it.

180
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:24,700
Be careful.

181
00:09:30,710 --> 00:09:31,680
Xu Hanzhi,

182
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,090
do you still hate me?

183
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:35,330
I never have.

184
00:09:36,910 --> 00:09:38,360
You ate the Autumn Frost Grass,

185
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:39,480
and now your internal organs are torn apart.

186
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,180
What if you die?

187
00:09:43,930 --> 00:09:45,550
I tested the medicine for you

188
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,190
and found the antidote.

189
00:09:47,650 --> 00:09:49,140
I'll die without regret.

190
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:51,110
Die without regret?

191
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:53,330
You make it sound easy.

192
00:09:54,610 --> 00:09:56,220
If I die,

193
00:09:56,820 --> 00:09:58,040
would you be sad?

194
00:09:58,490 --> 00:09:59,670
No.

195
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,490
Because I won't let you die.

196
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:12,690
Then I have one more question.

197
00:10:15,110 --> 00:10:16,530
Do you have me in your heart?

198
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:19,460
Back then, I used the Southern Yue secret technique to restore your appearance,

199
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,150
but I left this slave mark,

200
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:23,620
just to remind you of your place.

201
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,390
No.

202
00:10:44,590 --> 00:10:46,090
Tomorrow morning, when he wakes up,

203
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,870
his vision will be restored.

204
00:10:48,190 --> 00:10:49,570
I have to say something to you.

205
00:10:49,810 --> 00:10:51,980
You are in worse condition than Xu Hanzhi,

206
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,900
yet you were running around looking for a cure for him.

207
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,120
The poison in your body

208
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,770
has already entered your veins.

209
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:59,000
Can you worry about your own safety?

210
00:11:00,130 --> 00:11:01,580
As long as he recovers.

211
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:02,470
It doesn't matter.

212
00:11:04,620 --> 00:11:05,610
You...

213
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,360
If you

214
00:11:07,380 --> 00:11:09,300
survive the next two days,

215
00:11:09,450 --> 00:11:10,320
you should

216
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,500
go to Southern Yue.

217
00:11:11,530 --> 00:11:12,500
Their royal family

218
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,180
has a way to cure your poison.

219
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:14,790
However,

220
00:11:14,810 --> 00:11:16,030
it's just a rumor.

221
00:11:16,050 --> 00:11:17,080
The chances are slim.

222
00:11:17,530 --> 00:11:18,500
If it doesn't work,

223
00:11:18,530 --> 00:11:20,320
next year I'll pull the grass off your grave.

224
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:24,750
Thank you, Sir.

225
00:11:24,940 --> 00:11:26,150
It's just a small favor.

226
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,360
You may leave now.

227
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,350
Just leave Si here.

228
00:11:44,370 --> 00:11:45,120
Yes.

229
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:45,900
Yes.

230
00:12:11,580 --> 00:12:12,670
What are you doing?
